title: Wes Watson On Choosing Your Purpose Over Pleasure @GPPenitentiaryLifeWesWatson
description:
Here's a clip from my podcast episode with Wes Watson
Full Video 🔗: https://youtu.be/bLRvlOFKfgg

​Wes Watson (IG: @Watson_Fit) is an inspirational speaker, fitness trainer, and ex-convict. He did a 10-year term in the Californian penitentiary system for an aggravated assault related to drug dealing. He currently posts videos on his youtube channel @GPPenitentiaryLifeWesWatson about stories from when he was in prison and the lessons he learned from them. Wes has an online fitness program called Watson Fit.
